Alexandre Brasseur https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alexandre_Brasseur 0 Alexandre Brasseur (born Alexandre Espinasse on 29 March 1971) is a French actor. He was born in Neuilly-sur-Seine, the son of actor Claude Brasseur and the grandson of actor Pierre Brasseur. Alexandre_Brasseur ( born Alexandre_Espinasse on 29_March_1971 ) is a_French_actor .
